    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      IssuanceBuilder()
      Create a IssuanceBuilder for building PolicyPeriods with the following defaults:

      Newly created Account with DistributionLimitType of 'Up to Amount Under Contract' Billing Method of 'Direct Bill' Single Premium Charge of 1000 of the builder's currency Newly created Primary Producer Code with 'On Payment Received' Payable Criteria and 10% rate BoundDate = today Payment Plan = Default Policy Closure Status = Open Effective Date = today Expiration Date = today plus one year Product (LOB) = PersonalAuto

      Use the builder methods to change any of these defaults.

    • Constructor Detail

      • IssuanceBuilder

        public IssuanceBuilder()
        Create a IssuanceBuilder for building PolicyPeriods with the following defaults:

        • Newly created Account with DistributionLimitType of 'Up to Amount Under Contract'
        • Billing Method of 'Direct Bill'
        • Single Premium Charge of 1000 of the builder's currency
        • Newly created Primary Producer Code with 'On Payment Received' Payable Criteria and 10% rate
        • BoundDate = today
        • Payment Plan = Default
        • Policy Closure Status = Open
        • Effective Date = today
        • Expiration Date = today plus one year
        • Product (LOB) = PersonalAuto

        Use the builder methods to change any of these defaults.
